Class MapData

  • java.lang.Object
    • za.ac.mandela.WRPV301.Capstone.Map.MapData
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    com.google.common.graph.MutableNetwork<MapLocation,​Accessway>, com.google.common.graph.Network<MapLocation,​Accessway>, com.google.common.graph.PredecessorsFunction<MapLocation>, com.google.common.graph.SuccessorsFunction<MapLocation>
    public class MapData
extends java.lang.Object
implements com.google.common.graph.MutableNetwork<MapLocation,​Accessway>
    Wrapper class for MutableNetwork that is grid-addressable and provides convenience methods for common graph operations.

      • distributeKeys

        private void distributeKeys()
        Distributes a chain of keys for rooms, each of which is a maze dead end, and holds the key for the next such room. Rooms are chosen heuristically, namely the second closest by Pythagorean distance
